{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"double","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:d"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"zoomLevel","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In addition to affecting the visual size and detail of features on the map,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the zoom level affects the size of the vector tiles that are loaded. At zoom"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"level 0, each tile covers the entire world map; at zoom level 1, it covers ¼"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the world; at zoom level 2, "},{"type":"text","text":"1"},{"type":"text","text":"⁄"},{"type":"text","text":"16"},{"type":"text","text":" of the world, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"so on."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view immediately. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to animate the change, use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setZoomLevel:animated:"},{"type":"text","text":" method instead."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/zoomlevel"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1007"},"symbolKind":"property","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"zoomLevel","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"zoomLevel","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"zoomLevel","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:obj